flowchart TB
    CTRL["Controller event stream<br/>(one WebSocket upstream)"]

    subgraph Web ["Web server"]
        Fanout["fanout bus"]
        Buffer["rolling in-memory buffer<br/>(N=200 per scope)"]
    end

    B1["browser 1"]
    B2["browser 2"]
    B3["browser 3"]

    CTRL --> Fanout
    Fanout <--> Buffer
    Fanout -- "per-browser SSE<br/>(filtered by principal,<br/>SRD-0114 D10)" --> B1
    Fanout --> B2
    Fanout --> B3

    Note["INV-WEB-EVENT-FANOUT-UPSTREAM-ONE:<br/>at most one upstream subscription<br/>per scope-family"]
    CTRL -.-> Note

    classDef ctrl fill:#e8f0ff,stroke:#3366aa
    classDef web fill:#fff4e0,stroke:#aa7733
    classDef client fill:#e8ffe8,stroke:#338833
    classDef inv fill:#f0f0f0,stroke:#666
    class CTRL ctrl
    class Fanout,Buffer web
    class B1,B2,B3 client
    class Note inv
